content: Back in NYC after an unforgettable time in Japan. The energy here is electric, but I'm missing the tranquility. Time to unpack and get back into the swing of things.

content: Spent the morning setting up my new desk. It's strange not having the view of Mount Fuji, but the skyline of NYC has its own charm.
